data.name: The Perfect Sketchbook - Interlace
data.description:
The Perfect Sketchbook was born from a request to create the finest quality sketchbook for artists. A number of prominent artists were invited to try out The Perfect Sketchbook and their sketches were fitted in custom frames designed by Bynd Artisan and put on display. INTERLACE celebrates these talented individuals from around the world who have extensive experience in renowned companies such as Walt Disney, Marvel Studios, and DreamWorks. Our video captures the rawness and beauty of the fine arts and the passionate community that this project brought together.
